# May 2026 Astrology Notes

## May 13-31

This note is a working journal for the May 13-31, 2026 stretch.

The bigger backdrop is still the same: you are in a Uranus-on-Mercury phase. That can feel brilliant, disruptive, overstimulating, clarifying, and slightly unhinged all at once. The point is not to force yourself into a calm, linear version of thinking if that is not the weather right now. The point is to notice what is changing in your voice, mind, pace, and identity, and to gather enough evidence from your lived experience that the future version of `ohmie` can give you guidance that is actually yours.

## How To Use This

- Read the day you are on.
- Add notes even if they are messy or short.
- If you miss a day, do not backfill perfectly. Just pick back up.
- If something repeats, note it. Repetition is data.

## What To Notice This Month

- nervous system patterns
- sleep and dreams
- body tension or grounding
- writing and idea flow
- irritation, urgency, or overstimulation
- relationship triggers
- moments of clarity, relief, or alignment

